<div class="page-header">
  <h2>Delivery Request summary</h2>
</div>
<div class="row-fluid">
  <div class="span4">
    <div class="alert alert-info center lead">
      CERES has been notified of your Delivery Request!
    </div>
    <h3>Congratulations</h3>
    <p class="justify">
      You will receive a confirmation email containing further instructions at: <%= mail_to @delivery_request.email, @delivery_request.email, encode: :hexl %>
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="span5">
    <div class="well well-large" >
      <div style="max-width: 340px; margin: auto;">
        <%= link_to raw('Download Delivery Request Form summary (PDF)&nbsp;<i class="icon-download-alt"></i>'),
          joomla_delivery_request_pdf_url(@delivery_request, subdomain: 'request', format: :pdf), class: "btn btn-large btn-block btn-success" %>
        <%= link_to 'Create a new Delivery Request', new_joomla_delivery_request_path, class: "btn btn-large btn-block btn-info" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="span9">
 <!--   <p class="lead">
    TODO: Je peux mettre le texte ci desous seulement s'il y a
    plus de 50 modules.</p>
-->
    <p class="justify">
    Please note that the modules must be stored on pallets that should respect
    the following guidelines:<br /> The pallets must be:
    <ul>
      <li>
      Covered with plastic wrap
      </li>
      <li>
      Not taller that 1.25m, including the pallet
      </li>
      <li>
      Stackables
      </li>
    </ul>
    </p>
    <p class="justify">
    Your request will be transmitted to the Collection Point below, who will
    contact you under 72hrs to arrange the delivery:
    </p>
    <h3>Delivery Request summary</h3>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="span5">
        <h4>Collection Point</h4>
        <% unless @delivery_request.collection_point.nil? %>
          You will be contacted under 72hrs by the following Collection Point:
        <br />
        <br />
        <address>
          <strong><%= @delivery_request.collection_point.name %></strong><br>
          <%= @delivery_request.collection_point.address %><br>
          <%= "#{@delivery_request.collection_point.postal_code}, #{@delivery_request.collection_point.city}" %><br>
          <%= @delivery_request.collection_point.country %>
        </address>
        <br />
        Who will discuss the operational details with you.
      <% else %>
          Sorry, no Collection Point were found in your area. CERES will come back to you under 72hrs to check for an adequate solution
      <% end %>
        <h4>Modules information</h4>
        <table class="table table-bordered">
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td class="strong">Number of Modules</td>
              <td><%= @delivery_request.module_count %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="strong">Technology</td>
              <td><%= @delivery_request.humanized_delivery_requests_technologies %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="strong">Production year</td>
              <td><%= @delivery_request.modules_production_year %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="strong">Number of pallets</td>
              <td><%= @delivery_request.pallets_number %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="strong">Weight</td>
              <td><%= @delivery_request.weight %></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
